Author: meVu
Title: [ANN|ITO] meVu.bet - P2P Network to Bet on Anything, Anytime, Against Anyone!
Body: We are building the platform and network to facilitate a system of peer-to-peer betting, which allows users to compete directly and requires less dependence on third-parties than traditional systems currently do. Our focus is keeping bets 1v1 and on single events, not group bets on multiple events. Also unlike our "competitors" our bets will be placed in ETH allowing for liquidity on the platform and ease of use instead of requiring our "native" token to be used just to bet. This makes it easier for bets to be placed and accepted. Finally we do not cut corners and have taken time to build our community out organically and naturally. We have spent $0 to date on marketing once we do we will have a bigger "real community" and not have to rely on bots.

Author: Mith19
Title: [ANN|ITO] meVu.bet - P2P Network to Bet on Anything, Anytime, Against Anyone!
Body: Jap, the communication and the transfer of information is really shitty. And it's quite obvious, why they are not showing any tendency to talk about it. I think they were quite overwhelmed by the big demand (understandable, it is a nice project) during their pre-ITO, which was closed a long time before the announced deadline --> which is fine, when you were to slow, it's your problem, nothing to argue about. But then apparently they started to wonder why they are giving away their tokens so cheap, given the big interest which was already there during pre-ITO. So they increased the prices of the main token sale without attracting any attention to it. Apparently they were hoping that nobody will complain because nobody will realize it (and people who are already invested made via this already insanely gains, so of course, they will also not complain).  I just want to stress what this means whith an easy example:  - Person A invests 1000$ in the main tokensale (first stage, token price is 0.4$)  - Person A gets 2500 tokens  - Person B invested 1000$ during the pre-ITO  - Person B got 20.000 tokens  So persons who invested in the pre-ITO have have gotten a bonus of additional 700%!  700%, this is insane.  I saw people complaining at some ICOs about bonuses of 50%, but compared to 700%, this is merely kindergarden.

Author: meVu
Title: [ANN|ITO] meVu.bet - P2P Network to Bet on Anything, Anytime, Against Anyone!
Body: I understand where the concern is coming from, and apologize for the way you are feeling. We needed to make the change to the price of the token as long term business decision.  Our lead investor (global blockchain) found us with out us having spent any $$ on marketing. We met them in person, showed them our prototype and shook on a deal. Global blockchain purchased our token along with 30% equity at an average of 8c USD/MVU. Global blockchain will provide the funds needed to compete for the attention in this space but will bring a lot more then just capital to the table. Not only will development be expedited but key connections, and partnerships will be announced in the coming weeks/months, that would not of been possible otherwise.  With GBC we feel more confident in being able to gain early traction, adding the needed liquidity on our platform, and exceeding the expectations we have set out.  Previously our raise was only for 7MM USD in the public sale, and after discussions with GBC, our advisors, and executives from traditional or "legacy" sports books 7 MM is just not enough to compete.  We want to be here in 3-5 years when the mainstream begins adopting crypto and blockchain tech and see meVu as a trusted, fun and established dapp. This is why we raised the starting price in the public sale to 40c with 60MM MVU available for a sale targeting a 24 Mil USD raise, which in our opinion is still a very modest.  This will allow us to become a self sustaining and established brand for the future.  Once again we do apologize for the change at such a late time, but we needed to adapt our plan for future success. We have been busy at work and I apologize for not being as active as we should be on this forum. Gearing up for our marketing campaign April 1st and have many things to get organized prior too. I check telegram 24/7 and you can join our group here https://t.me/joinchat/FKcKRUwJ1_T8zMK2Lueu3A Alternatively you can always email me kelvin@mevu.bet and I will be sure to answer ASAP. Thank you for your interest in meVu, and I hope you understand our decision and continue participating in our community.

Title: [ANN|ITO] meVu.bet - P2P Network to Bet on Anything, Anytime, Against Anyone!
Body: meVu.bet Official Bounty Campaign Thread    The Bounty Campaign will run from January 13th - July 16th The Pre-Sale will run from January 22nd - March 14th The Public Sale will run from June 11th - July 16th  For the Bitcointalk Bounty Campaign, meVu has reserved 2% of the total token supply to be distributed to participants. MEVU are ERC20 Tokens which are being sold during the pre-sale and public sale until July 16th! MEVU Tokens will be distributed among the participants in the campaign based on shares earned in each bounty component, given the predetermined allocations for each as seen below.  Bounty Components 1. Telegram Campaign ‚Äì 5% 2. Translation Campaign ‚Äì 20% 3. Social Media Campaign (Facebook/Twitter) ‚Äì 45% 4. Article/Media Campaign ‚Äì 10% 5. Signature Campaign ‚Äì 20%  IMPORTANT: Once a participants registers with an ETH Address, do not change address throughout the campaign! Only provide ETH address to which you know the private keys or seed phrases. (No exchanges, Shapeshift, or other 3rd party services).  We look forward to having the support of the Bitcointalk Community and rewarding you all for your work with meVu Tokens (MEVU) an ERC20 token designed for the meVu P2P betting platform. Be sure to check out https://www.mevu.bet/ to learn more!    1. meVu Telegram Campaign ‚Äì 5%  Rewards: ‚Ä¢ Telegram Channel Registration: 1 Share  Guidelines: To earn 1 Share, all you need to do is join our official Telegram channel and fill out the form below. You must remain in the Telegram channel until conclusion of the token offering! Each participant can earn a maximum of 1 Share in this component of the campaign.  How To Apply: Join our Telegram Group Telegram/Newsletter Registration Form  Check Telegram Spreadsheet: Here   2. meVu Translation Campaign ‚Äì 35%  Announcement Thread Link Whitepaper Link  Rewards: ‚Ä¢ Whitepaper Translation: 125 Shares ‚Ä¢ Whitepaper Updates: 15 Shares Each Update ‚Ä¢ ANN Thread Translation: 100 Shares ‚Ä¢ ANN Thread Updates: 2 Shares Each Post  Guidelines: ‚Ä¢ Absolutely no google translator is permitted to be used. Participants using google translator will not be accepted and if a google translation is submitted, that translator will be blacklisted! ‚Ä¢ Participants may only translate in one language, but can translate both the whitepaper and the announcement thread. ‚Ä¢ Please do not submit a request to translate unless you are fluent in the translated language and in English. ‚Ä¢ Announcement Thread translators are expected to moderate the thread and regularly update the thread with news, info, posts, etc from the original meVu Ann Thread or social medias. Each post will earn an additional 2 shares! ‚Ä¢ If Announcement Thread translators do not make a reasonable attempt to regularly update the thread, a 75% reduction in share will be applied! (75 Shares!). Make minimum 2 updates per week and this reduction will not apply! ‚Ä¢ Do not begin translating until we have approved your reservation! ‚Ä¢ Managers/Owners reserve the right to make minor, reasonable changes to the rules.  How to Apply: To reserve a language, please post your interest along with some of your references following the following format:  ‚Ä¢ Your Language: ‚Ä¢ Reference to previous works (at least 3): ‚Ä¢ Translating Whitepaper, ANN thread or both:  Once accepted, you will be contacted by PM by the meVu BCTalk Account and we will post a list of accepted translators here.  Current Translations:    3. meVu Social Media Campaign ‚Äì 25%  Official meVu Twitter Official meVu Facebook  Rewards: ‚Ä¢ 2 Shares / 1 Tweet about meVu ‚Ä¢ 1 Shares / 1 Retweet of meVu account tweet ‚Ä¢ 2 Shares / 1 Facebook Post about meVu ‚Ä¢ 1 Shares / 1 Facebook Share of meVu account post  Check Facebook Spreadsheet: Here Check Twitter Spreadsheet: Here  Guidelines:  Twitter: ‚Ä¢ You must first follow @mevu_bet. ‚Ä¢ One twitter account per bitcoin talk member is allowed. ‚Ä¢ Your twitter account must have at least 300 authentic followers. ‚Ä¢ All tweets will be reviewed by bounty campaign managers. ‚Ä¢ Twitter Audit must be better than 80% (No Bot Behavior) ‚Ä¢ Maximum 5 Retweets Weekly ‚Ä¢ Maximum 5 Tweets Weekly ‚Ä¢ Maximum 15 Shares Earned Per Week! ‚Ä¢ A Tweet must include at least one hashtag: #meVu #meVuBET  Facebook: ‚Ä¢ Follow and like the official meVu Facebook page ‚Ä¢ One facebook account per bitcoin talk member is allowed. ‚Ä¢ Your facebook account must have at least 500 friends. ‚Ä¢ All posts AND profiles will be reviewed by bounty campaign managers. ‚Ä¢ Maximum 5 Posts Weekly ‚Ä¢ Maximum 5 Facebook Shares Weekly ‚Ä¢ Maximum 15 Shares Earned Per Week! ‚Ä¢ Posts and Profile must be public.  In order to submit claims, kindly fill in your weekly report forms here: Weekly Twitter Report Form (January 12th ‚Äì January 18th) Weekly Facebook Report Form (January 12th ‚Äì January 18th)  How to Apply: Twitter Registration Form Facebook Registration Form   4. Articles/Media Campaign ‚Äì 15%  Rewards: Articles/blog posts will earn 10, 20 or 30 Shares depending on the views, effort level and quality of the post, at the discretion of the meVu team.  Guidelines: ‚Ä¢ All articles or blog posts must be publicly viewable. ‚Ä¢ Listing on an ICO tracking / ICO schedule website will earn 30 Shares. ‚Ä¢ The platform through which you publish must be relevant and there must be an audience. ‚Ä¢ Pieces should be at least 400 words and include the links to our website (https://www.mevu.bet) and whitepaper (https://www.mevu.bet/#whitepaper) ‚Ä¢ Videos must be at least 1:00 long. Videos under this limit will not be accepted. ‚Ä¢ In the description of the video, there must be at least one link to the website and one link to the whitepaper.  How to Apply: Article/Media Registration Form  Check Article/Media Campaign Spreadsheet: Here   5. Signature Campaign ‚Äì 25%  Rewards: 1. Jr. Member: 15 Shares/Week 2. Member: 20 Sharess/Week 3. Full Member: 30 Shares/Week 4. Sr. Member: 50 Shares/Week 5: Hero Member: 65 Shares/Week 6: Legendary Member: 80 Shares/Week  +5 Shares/Week for wearing our Avatar!  Guidelines: ‚Ä¢ Must make at least 7 constructive posts on Bitcoin Talk Forum per week. ‚Ä¢ No negative trust accounts please  How to Apply: Signature Campaign Registration Form  The Bounty Manager will update spreadsheets every week and check that the signature is still being used week after week. The first campaign week runs from January 8th ‚Äì January 14th.
